        # ou-ghi0-awsccccc is an OU ID, and ou-jkl0-awsddddd is a child OU ID. IPAM will not manage the IP
        # addresses in accounts in the child OU. Example 2 Path where all child OUs will be part of the
        # exclusion: o-a1b2c3d4e5/r-f6g7h8i9j0example/ou-ghi0-awsccccc/* In this example, IPAM will not manage
